Issues.Body:
When FlowDocument.EndInit is called, the FontFamily gets changed.

Minimal reproduction:
```
            FlowDocument doc = new FlowDocument();
            var fontFamily = doc.FontFamily;

            doc.BeginInit();
            doc.EndInit();

            Assert.AreEqual(doc.FontFamily, fontFamily);
```

It should be _Segoe UI_ but after EndInit it changes to _Georgia_.

I managed to reproduce this both in .net 5 and 4.8

_This issue has been moved from [a ticket on Developer Community](https://developercommunity2.visualstudio.com/t/Erreur-de-type-dans-SystemWindowsMedia/1264233?preview=true)._

